text: Aamir Kaleem was born 20 November, 1981 in Karachi, Pakistan. He is an Oman cricketer who played 3 One-day Internationals and 29 Twenty20 Internationals for Oman. ==Other websites== * * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Omani cricketers Category:Cricketers from Karachi
title: Aamir Kaleem
